Package: replicaToolkitR
Type: Package
Title: Easily query and process data from Replica Mobility Platform
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mike Gaunt <mike.gaunt.404@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Mike Gaunt <mike.gaunt.404@gmail.com>
Description: replicaToolkitR automates the quering, processing, and analysis of Replica mobility data.
    Easily query Replica database using your inputs and own custom geometries.
    Use package functions to process queried data to build your analysis off of. 
    Create interactive, filerable map widgets to further inspect, slice, and extract information from your data.
